    <h1>New beginners cycle — March 2026</h1>
    <p class="news-meta">January 28, 2026</p>

    <p>
      In March we start a new Aikido cycle for beginners.
      The program is structured to build a safe and durable foundation.
    </p>

    <h2>Who is it for?</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>people without previous martial arts experience,</li>
      <li>practitioners returning after a longer break,</li>
      <li>anyone who wants to start from strong fundamentals.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What does it include?</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>movement basics and safe ukemi,</li>
      <li>introduction to dojo etiquette (reishiki),</li>
      <li>first technical forms and partner work.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      First class is free. See organizational details on the
      <a href="/en/contact.html">Contact</a> page.
    </p>
